text: Paule Moris (born 28 December 1932) is a French alpine skier. She competed in two events at the 1956 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1932 births Category:Living people Category:French female alpine skiers Category:Olympic alpine skiers of France Category:Alpine skiers at the 1956 Winter Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Savoie
